{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ballbastic! is a game created to scratch the itch of hardcore gamers with an interest in games that are easy to learn but difficult to master.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your rolling skills against 150 levels across Novice, Journeyman, Expert, and Marathon Mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">See how fast you can beat a difficulty level when you select Play for Time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">See how far you can get on a single life in Survival Mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shake up your experience with Randomizer Mode after beating every level once.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn how to utilize your environment with trampolines, rockets, teleporters, speeders, slowers, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel through harder-to-reach warps to skip levels!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Six different worlds, all with their own theme, from the simple mountains to the mind-boggling dreamscape. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Instantaneous gameplay</strong>. No instant replays when you die or score calculations when you pass a level--just keep on going!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Featuring Brian Matt as the announcer; returning to form from narrating Super Monkey Ball games in the early 2000s.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/BrianMatt_4_.jpg?t=1738378431\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Different types of cosmetic skins to unlock that prove what you are capable of doing!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/Ball_Types.png?t=1738378431\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Controller support!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ticking Away","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/